  "metadata": {
    "modules": [
      {
        "name": "Core Spotlight"
      }
    ],
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Regenerating your app’s indexes on demand"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Keeping your app’s indexes up to date requires periodic maintenance.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "An app that crashes while updating its index might leave that index",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in an incorrect state. The system can also ask your app to regenerate",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the index if it’s missing or needs updated data. If your app",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "isn’t running when the system needs these updates, it uses your",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "reindexing app extension to generate them instead.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A reindexing app extension is an important tool for keeping your indexes",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "up to date at all times. Include this app extension in your app bundle,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and make sure it has access to all of your app’s indexable data.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-a-reindexing-app-extension-to-your-app",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add a reindexing app extension to your app",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Xcode provides a template to make it easy to add a reindexing app extension",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to your app. Add this template to your project using the following steps:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Open the Xcode project with your app.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select File > New > Target.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select the platform for your app.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "In the Application Extension section, select the CoreSpotlight Delegate template.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click Next.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Give your app extension a name and configure the other options.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click Finish.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The CoreSpotlight Delegate template contains empty implementations for the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "key functions of the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.corespotlight/documentation/CoreSpotlight/CSSearchableIndexDelegate",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " protocol, including",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the methods you use to update the index. Add your custom code to these",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "methods, and make sure to call the acknowledgement handlers for your main",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "indexing functions, as shown:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "import CoreSpotlight",
            "",
            "class MyIndexingExtension: CSIndexExtensionRequestHandler {",
            "",
            "    override func searchableIndex(_ searchableIndex: CSSearchableIndex, ",
            "                  reindexAllSearchableItemsWithAcknowledgementHandler acknowledgementHandler: @escaping () -> Void) {",
            "        // Index everything.",
            "        acknowledgementHandler()",
            "    }",
            "",
            "    override func searchableIndex(_ searchableIndex: CSSearchableIndex, ",
            "                  reindexSearchableItemsWithIdentifiers identifiers: [String], ",
            "                  acknowledgementHandler: @escaping () -> Void) {",
            "        // Index the specified items.",
            "        acknowledgementHandler()",
            "    }",
            "",
            "    // Other methods.",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For information about how to add content to your app’s indexes, see",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.corespotlight/documentation/CoreSpotlight/adding-your-app-s-content-to-spotlight-indexes",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Debug-your-app-extension-code",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Debug your app extension code",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Verify your app extension behaves as expected using the Xcode debugger.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Start by building your app extension and attaching the debugger to it.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select your app target",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Build and run your app.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Back in Xcode, select your app extension target.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Select Debug > Attach to Process by PID or Name.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Set the name of the process to the bundle ID of your app extension.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Click the Attach button.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Because you can’t predict when the system will run your app extension,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you need to force the system to run it immediately using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "mdutil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "command-line tool. Open Terminal and run that command with the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "-cr",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "option, followed by the bundle identifier of your app extension.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Here’s an example of this command:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "code": "mdutil -cr com.example.MyApp.MyIndexingExtension",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "mdutil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " tool starts the reindexing process for the app extension",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you specify. If you set any breakpoints in your app extension’s code,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the attached debugger stops at them and gives you a chance to examine",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the state of your extension.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
